<P>ORDERED, That MOSES GILL, HENRY GARDNER, and TI|MOTHY DANIELSON, E&s;q'rs; be a Committee to wait on the Rev'd. Mr. SAMUEL-PHILLIPS PAYSON, and return him the Thanks of the Board for his SER|MON delivered Ye&s;terday, before both Hou&s;es of A&s;&s;embly; and re|que&s;t a Copy thereof for the Pre&s;s.</P>
